'''Tabitha''' is [[Molly]]'s girlfriend and partner, played by [[Carly Thomas Smith]]. 

Tabitha arrives at the last minute in "[[The One With Phoebe's Rats]]", and kisses Molly, leading to a disappointed [[Joey Tribbiani|Joey]], who has a crush on Molly. We only see Tabitha for about 2 seconds and she doesn't reappear.
